race.comment: GREEN SPACES (3) Street Boss colt peaking at the right time. Was a comfortable winner in a small field over 1625m at Wyong last time out and looks ready for this stiffer test from the good gate. Rachel King sticks and is only one of a few with a win at the trip. GRAND PRAIRIE (1) proven at this level having won the G3 Up & Coming three starts back. Plagued by wide draws at the last two runs and should get every chance to see this trip out with regular rider aboard. ROSA INCANTA (9) sharp filly heading in the right direction. Taken straight to the front here at latest when a commanding winner over 1300m in the soft conditions. Big drop in weight and will give a good account of herself out in trip. Top-three player. PROBABILITY THEORY (8) improving filly chasing the hat-trick. Won't get the same favours today from the draw after looking the goods when scoring over 1300m at Hawkesbury in fast time. From a So You Think mare and stays in the mix. VERITY (10) respect with the blinkers added.
